import moment from 'moment' const Div = ({ padding, dataResponse, num }) => { const data = { weather: "", icon: "", temp: 0, feels_like: 0, temp_min: 0, temp_max: 0, pressure: 0, humidity: 0, visibility: 0, windsSpeed: 0, sunrise: "", sunset: "", } const round = (num) => { return Math.round(num * 100) / 100; }; data.push( {weather: dataResponse.obj[num].weather, icon: dataResponse.obj[num].icon, temp: round(dataResponse.obj[num].temp - 273.15), feels_like: round(dataResponse.obj[num].feels_like - 273.15), pressure: dataResponse.obj[num].pressure, temp_min: round(dataResponse.obj[num].temp_min - 273.15), temp_max: round(dataResponse.obj[num].temp_max - 273.15), humidity: dataResponse.obj[num].humidity, visibility: dataResponse.obj[num].visibility, windSpeed: dataResponse.obj[num].speedSpeed, sunrise: moment(dataResponse.obj[num].sunrise * 1e3) .format("hh:mm a") .toString(), sunset: moment(dataResponse.obj[num].sunset * 1e3) .format("hh:mm a") .toString(),}) return (
Tiempo: {data.weather}
{data.icon ? (
) : null}
Temperatura: {data.temp}
Sensación Térmica: {data.feels_like}
Temperatura Mínima: {data.temp_min}
Temperatura Máxima: {data.temp_max}
Presión: {data.pressure}
Humedad: {data.humidity}
Visibilidad: {data.visibility}
Velocidad de viento: {data.windSpeed}
Amanecer: {data.sunrise}
Atardecer: {data.sunset}
); }; export default Div
